name: Calculus of Several Variables
description: "Bridging Course"; accepted as prerequisite for upper level courses in replacement of MAT232H5. Limited Enrolment. Sequences and series, power series, Taylor series, trigonometric and inverse trigonometric functions and their use in integrations. Differential and integral calculus of several variables; partial differentiation, chain rule, extremal problems, Lagrange multipliers, classification of critical points. Multiple integrals, Green's theorem and related topics. [48L, 12T]
exclusions: MAT232H5, MAT235Y1, MAT237Y1, MAT257Y1, MAT257Y5, MATB41H3
